United Arab Emirates Inflation Slows to Annual 0.6% in August

-- B y   G l e n   C a r e y
-- 
2011-09-17T09:25:12Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-17/united-arab-emirates-inflation-slows-to-annual-0-6-in-august.html
Inflation in the  United Arab
Emirates  slowed to 0.6 percent in August from 1.3 percent in the
previous month, the National Bureau of Statistics said in an e-
mailed statement today. The cost of living index declined 0.1
percent in August from July, it said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Glen Carey in Riyadh at 
 gcarey8@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Digby Lidstone at 
 dlidstone@bloomberg.net  